metadata.name: Under the Black Sun 1
metadata.description:
Under the Black Sun is where demons live. It's a dark beauty aesthetic that I want to convey to other people. I create my Dark Queens with paint, brushes, shadows and a camera in my studio.

This photograph has won 9 awards (The International Photography Awards 2021, Fine Art Photography Awards 2021, ND Awards 2021, Annual Photography Awards 2020 etc).
